divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking photos of a storm that was moving into the area. I was standing in a WalMart parking lot in Downers Grove, IL. I did not load these photos onto my computer until a couple of months later. When I was loking at the photos I noticed something on one of them and my first thought was, "What is that?" I zoomed in on the object and it is definitely not a bird or an airplane. I will submit the photo to you for you to look at. I have submitted it to NUFORC before. I just found this website and thought I would submit it to you. This is not my first experience of sightings. I could tell you many stories my family and I have had with sightings of UFO's. There have been some I would give anything to be able to go back and experience and have a camera with me to catch it on film. The photo I will attach will be normal and an inverted one. The inverted one will show the UFO in white against the dark sky.
Summary: Captured UFO unknowingly while taking photos of storm clouds
trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Downers Grove
There were no other sightings in Downers Grove on or around May 15th 2007
